snippet.description:
#Fighter releasing in cinemas on 25th January worldwide. Experience it in IMAX 3D. 
#FighterTrailer #FighterMovie 

Film Credits: 
Movie: Fighter 
Starring: Hrithik Roshan, Deepika Padukone, Anil Kapoor, Karan Singh Grover, Akshay Oberoi 
Director: Siddharth Anand

Viacom18 Studios Team

Syndication: Gayatri Gulati 
Business Planning & Content Alliances: Pradeep Prabhu

Synopsis:
Militant activities are going out of control in the Srinagar Valley, so a new and elite unit, Air Dragons, is commissioned by the Air Headquarters. They are now the first responders to any hostile activity. They comprise of the best combat aviators handpicked from across the IAF. FIGHTER is the story of Air Dragons who are willing to give it their all for the nation while going through the highs and lows of their internal and external battles.

snippet.title: Maldives is INSULTING India, again? | Maldives vs Lakshadweep | Abhi and Niyu
snippet.description:
In this video, Abhi and Niyu explore the relationship between Maldives and Lakshadweep. Recently, prime minister Modi asked all Indians to visit India before they go abroad. But there is one major problem that India needs to address before we can boycott Maldives.

#geopolitics #lakshadweep #abhiandniyu

snippet.description:
Today, in our village, we cook 15 varieties of vegetarian recipes for the special Tamil day of the Pongal festival. We cook South Indian Veg thali recipes by cooking the following recipes: Rice, Sambar, Rasam, Mor, Payasam, Appalam, Vadai, Sweet Pongal, Potato fry, Lady Finger masala, Brinjal Masial, Raw banana Fry, Cabbage, Thandu Keerai Masiyal, and Pickle.

The taste is savory!

All the ladies of the Gokuldham Society are scared of the ghost. But the men refuse to believe it. The men decide to guard society at night to prove that there are no ghosts. Daya, according to her mother's advice, plans to send Jethalal to perform the task of getting rid of the ghost.

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: Manipur Commando Killed After Suspected Kuki Militants Launch Bombs, Rocket-Propelled Grenade
snippet.description:
A Manipur police commando was shot dead, allegedly by militants, in Moreh town on January 17. The slain commando has been identified as W. Somorjit. Militants fired rocket-propelled grenades on a camp of the commandos, near Ward 7 of Moreh. While one commando died, another sustained injuries, an official said. A government official aware of the matter said, "The gunfight lasted for almost an hour. The situation is tense." Watch this video to know more.

A Manipur police commando was shot dead, allegedly by militants, in Moreh town on January 17. The slain commando has been identified as W. Somorjit. Militants fired rocket-propelled grenades on a camp of the commandos, near Ward 7 of Moreh. While one commando died, another sustained injuries, an official said. A government official aware of the matter said, "The gunfight lasted for almost an hour. The situation is tense." Watch this video to know more.

--------------------------------------------------------
The men of Gokuldham search for Sodhi's friend, Sukhi. Together, they push the car, with Sodhi attempting to start it, but to no avail. The Gokuldham ladies grow concerned for their well-being. What will happen now?

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Main ATAL Hoon (Trailer 2) | Pankaj Tripathi | Ravi Jadhav | Vinod Bhanushali | 19 Jan 2024
snippet.description:
More than a poet. More than a statesman. More than a Prime Minister. Presenting trailer 2 of #MainATALHoon. 

Vinod Bhanushali presents, Main ATAL Hoon, a film on the extraordinary life of the leader you knew but the man you didn't, starring National Award winner Pankaj Tripathi. 

Directed by National Awardee Ravi Jadhav, and written by Rishi Virmani and Ravi Jadhav, "Main ATAL Hoon" produced by Bhanushali Studios Limited and Legend Studios, is produced by Vinod Bhanushali, Sandeep Singh, and Kamlesh Bhanushali.

The film releases on 19th January 2024 in cinemas near you. 


CREDITS:

Starring : Pankaj Tripathi
Director : Ravi Jadhav
Producers : Vinod Bhanushali, Sandeep Singh and Kamlesh Bhanushali
Co Producer - Bhavesh Bhanushali, Sam Khan

Mannat Murad Digitally Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Mannat is a beautiful young girl who hails from a progressive family that values love, care, and mutual respect. Raised in an environment where everyone's choices are respected, Mannat enjoys the freedom to make her own decisions. Following the untimely demise of her parents, she finds support from her elder brother, Nafees, who showers her with affection.

On the other hand, Murad belongs to a conservative family where his mother, the matriarch, wields significant influence over his life choices. As the only son, Murad is burdened with the responsibility of fulfilling his family's expectations. Soft-spoken and romantic by nature, Murad finds himself unable to defy his mother's authority, especially after the passing of his father.

Despite their starkly contrasting backgrounds, Mannat and Murad's hearts find solace in each other's presence, and they fall deeply in love. However, their families' interference creates misunderstandings between Mannat and Murad, testing the strength of their bond.

Will their families agree to their union? Will Mannat's family, with their open-mindedness, find common ground with Murad's conservative household? Can Mannat and Murad's love for each other withstand the motives of their families, who seek to create further misunderstandings between them?

snippet.title: SADAK SABHYATA | Gaurav Kapoor | Stand Up Comedy
snippet.description:
Hi Guys. This video has been brought to in association with NAGARRO with an objective increase awareness on the topic of SADAK SABHYATA. 
The video aims to put light on the fact that usually people, especially in vehicles, should be courteous towards pedestrians and cyclists on the road. 
This the most vulnerable group on the road since most of the infra is made for vehicular movement and pedestrians and cyclist have to use the same roads for their movement as well.
It‚Äôs a very basic civic sense and we should ensure that we are at least basic courteous toward pedestrians and cyclists, give them way, exercise road sense and awareness towards them.

I hope you like the video.
Thank you so much :)

Adi finds out about how Giriraj blackmailed Kavya to leave Adi. Kavya and Adi want to marry each other, and their mothers support their decision. However, their fathers are completely against their choices. What challenges will Kavya and Adi face now?

Sankranthi Middle Class Gaali Paatam from our Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu comes to wish everyone a Happy Pongal. In this new episode 1A master meet a director who came to Vizianagaram to conduct a Sankranti Event. 1A Master gathers all the colony families to participate in the event. Episode 3981: Bhide Gets His Things Back
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide pretends to be upset about his old belongings in front of Madhavi. However, Madhavi surprises him by returning his old stuff, expressing her newfound appreciation for the sentimental value attached to them. Later, Sukhi tells Sodhi that his car brings him good luck.

Mannat Murad 2nd Last Episode 32 - [Eng Sub] - Iqra Aziz - Talha Chahour - Digitally Presented by PEL - 15th January 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Mannat Murad Digitally Presented by PEL

Mannat is a beautiful young girl who hails from a progressive family that values love, care, and mutual respect. Raised in an environment where everyone's choices are respected, Mannat enjoys the freedom to make her own decisions. Following the untimely demise of her parents, she finds support from her elder brother, Nafees, who showers her with affection.

On the other hand, Murad belongs to a conservative family where his mother, the matriarch, wields significant influence over his life choices. As the only son, Murad is burdened with the responsibility of fulfilling his family's expectations. Soft-spoken and romantic by nature, Murad finds himself unable to defy his mother's authority, especially after the passing of his father.

Despite their starkly contrasting backgrounds, Mannat and Murad's hearts find solace in each other's presence, and they fall deeply in love. However, their families' interference creates misunderstandings between Mannat and Murad, testing the strength of their bond.

Will their families agree to their union? Will Mannat's family, with their open-mindedness, find common ground with Murad's conservative household? Can Mannat and Murad's love for each other withstand the motives of their families, who seek to create further misunderstandings between them?

Written by: Nadia Akhtar

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.
